Feature: Retrieve tests from Xray and store them as feature files

    As Xray Connector,
    I want to retrieve tests from Xray and store them as feature files
    So that the Test Automation Framework can execute them

    #  Rules:
    #
    # 1) Tests retrieved from Xray should be the ones linked to the configured test plan
    # 2) Feature files should be stored in the features download directory
    # 3) If the feature download directory does not exist it should be created
    # 4) Xray Connector should raise an error if the configured test plan does not exist in Xray
    # 5) Feature files that already exist may be overwritten
    # 6) Feature files left from previous executions should not be removed

    @xray
    Scenario: Retrieve feature files from Xray

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-48'
        And   The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/features'
        And   Directory 'tmp/cucumber' does not exist
        And   File 'tmp/cucumber/features/ACTIVE/1.feature' does not exist
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  File 'tmp/cucumber/features/ACTIVE/1.feature' should exist

    @xray
    Scenario: Handle non existing test plan

        Given The reference test plan is 'UNKNOWN'
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  An execution error should be reported

    @xray
    Scenario: Retrieve gatling test plan

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The test plan file is 'tmp/test-plan.json'
        And   Directory 'tmp' has been created
        When  Xray Connector retrieves feature files from Xray
        Then  File 'tmp/test-plan.json' should be the same as 'test/fixtures/test-plan.json'

