    Scenario: Retrieve gatling test plan from Jira respone

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The test plan file is 'tmp/test-plan.json'
        And   The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/features'
        And   Directory 'tmp' has been created

        When  Xray Connector gets test plan from 'test/fixtures/features/jira-test-plan-description.txt'

        Then  The test plan requests per second should be '10'
        And   The test plan min response time should be '800'
        And   The test plan max response time should be '3000'
        And   The test plan mean response time should be '2000'
        And   The test plan std dev response time should be '1000'
        And   The test plan 50th percentile response time should be '800'
        And   The test plan 75th percentile response time should be '1000'
        And   The test plan 95th percentile response time should be '1200'
        And   The test plan 99th percentile response time should be '1600'
        And   The test plan successful requests percent should be '100'

        And   The test plan should contain simulations
        And   The first simulation should contain steps
        And   The first simulation should specify tag 'test-tag'
        And   The first step should specify injection profile 'test-model-1'
        And   The first step should specify '2' users
        And   The first step should specify a duration of '123'

    Scenario: Retrieve empty gatling test plan from Jira empty respone

        Given The reference test plan is 'RDCHAPQA-45'
        And   The test plan file is 'tmp/test-plan.json'
        And   The feature files base directory is 'tmp/cucumber/features'
        And   Directory 'tmp' has been created

        When  Xray Connector gets test plan from 'test/fixtures/features/jira-test-plan-empty-description.txt'

        Then  The test plan should contain no simulation
